 He used his voice command on the computer. "The ship is run mostly on voice 
command. Mine alone. Then my hand print is put here." He pointed to a blank 
pad" which brings us in. A holographic view of the globe popped up. "What are 
the names of your colleagues? And you knew magnus when he began his group of 
joined factions from maximal to preds. Im sure you'll remember in time"

--part1_8a.afeb403.28ab52a3_boundary
